<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF226A9DF82092F619A9BED0" pageId="217" pageNumber="979" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF226A9DF82092F619A9BED0" blockId="217.[2007,2607,1041,1469]" lastBlockId="217.[1388,2604,1473,3243]" pageId="217" pageNumber="979">
Subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF226A9DF79292F616C3BFE2" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[2158,2243,1199,1232]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="217" pageNumber="979" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF226A9DF72992F61722BFE2" authorityName="Borkhausen" authorityYear="1797" box="[2261,2338,1199,1232]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="217" pageNumber="979" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="myotis">myotis</taxonomicName>
species group. 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF226A9DF60192F6142CBFE2" box="[2557,2604,1199,1232]" country="South Sudan" name="Lakes" pageId="217" pageNumber="979">See</collectingRegion>
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF226A9DF820928E1673BFCA" baseAuthorityName="Kuhl" baseAuthorityYear="1817" box="[2012,2163,1239,1272]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="217" pageNumber="979" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="nattereri">M. nattereri</taxonomicName>
. The name 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF226A9DF6EB928E17AEBFCA" baseAuthorityName="Kuhl" baseAuthorityYear="1817" box="[2327,2478,1239,1272]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="217" pageNumber="981" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="nattereri">M. nattereri</taxonomicName>
helverseni was recently proposed by E. Coraman and colleagues in 2019 based on populations that are now included under this species; the name is considered a nomen nudum as the publication did not include a proper description for the name. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
